OL,5, A former BBC radio presenter found     
OL,6, guilty of stalking four people         
OL,7, including broadcaster Jeremy Vine has  
OL,8, been jailed for five and a half years. 
OL,10,FAlex Belfield, who now runs a YouTube  
OL,11,Fchannel, stalked his victims by        
OL,12,Fharassing them online.                 
OL,14,FHis trial heard he made YouTube videos 
OL,15,Fabout them, posted messages on social  
OL,16,Fmedia, sent emails, and also encouraged
OL,17,Fhis followers to target them.          
OL,19,FThe judge said one of his victims was  
OL,20,F"seconds away" from killing himself.   
